    {
      "id": 40,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Anchor Data Source: FtsoV2 Smart Contract",
      "description": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 33,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Anchor Data Source\n\nThis dashboard compares our provider prices against the **Flare FTSOv2 on-chain anchor** -- the median of all provider submissions updated every ~90 seconds.\n\n**Data source:** FtsoV2 smart contract via getFeedsById() on Flare mainnet\n**Contract:** Resolved via ContractRegistry at 0xaD67FE66660Fb8dFE9d6b1b4240d8650e30F6019\n**RPC endpoint:** https://flare-api.flare.network/ext/C/rpc\n**Anchor deviation %** is the metric used for on-chain scoring."
      },
      "targets": []
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "External Verification & Known Limitations",
      "description": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 8,
        "y": 33,
        "w": 8,
        "h": 5
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## External Verification\n\n**Catenalytica Performance Dashboard**\n[Digital Dynamix (1h window)](https://catenalytica.com/dashboard/ftso-performance/overview/0x16C0619b2C427AaEb5931426eB0a898b6E3Cd885?timeWindow=1h&scoreType=primary&providers=Digital+Dynamix&sort=name)\n\n**Flare Systems Explorer**\n[FTSO Price Feeds](https://flare-systems-explorer.flare.network/price-feeds/ftso)\n\n## Known Limitations (Test Platform)\n\n| Limitation | Impact | What we show instead |\n|:---|:---|:---|\n| No direct mainnet access | Anchor may lag by 1-2 epochs | On-chain anchor contract call via Flare RPC |\n| Test provider instance | Not the production submission | Same codebase, same feeds, same calculation |\n| JOULE/USD missing | Only 63/64 feeds active | Bitrue source unresponsive -- documented in logs |\n| Binance spot gaps | 12 feeds not on Binance spot | CoinGecko + Anchor as primary refs |\n\n**What we do:** Every 30s we call getFeedsById() on Flare mainnet, compare against our local provider, and log the deviation. This dashboard reflects that live comparison."
      },
      "targets": []
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Last Voting Round",
      "description": "Most recent votingRoundId committed to by the provider. Updated when the Scaling client requests feed values for a specific round.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 16,
        "y": 33,
        "w": 4,
        "h": 5
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "colorMode": "background"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "none",
          "decimals": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
